<%= '<p class="text-1">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</p>' %>

<%= '<h2>BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h2>' %>
<%= '<p class="text-2">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</p>' %>

<%= '<h3>BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h3>' %>
<%= '<p class="text-3">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</p>' %>

<%= '<h4>BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h4>' %>
<%= '<p class="text-4">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</p>' %>

<%= '<h5>BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h5>' %>
<%= '<p class="text-5">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</p>' %>

<%= '<h6>BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h6>' %>
<%= '<p class="text-6">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</p>' %></code></pre>

</section>

<section class="xs-mb5 xs-pb2">

  <h2 class="xs-mb2 bold">Slab Headers</h2>

  <p class="xs-mb4">Caponi Slab Semibold is BuzzFeed News' headline typeface (please avoid any other usage). It can be applied to <code class="js-highlight">h1</code> through <code class="js-highlight">h5</code> and <span class="nowrap">.<code class="js-highlight">text-1</code></span> through <span class="nowrap">.<code class="js-highlight">text-5</code></span> using <span class="nowrap">.<code class="js-highlight">slab</code></span> .</p>

  <div class="xs-mb4">
    <p class="xs-mb1">.<code class="js-highlight">slab</code></p>
    <h1 class="slab xs-mb2">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h1>   
    <h2 class="slab xs-mb2">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h2>   
    <h3 class="slab xs-mb2">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h3>   
    <h4 class="slab xs-mb2">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h4>   
    <h5 class="slab">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h5>   
  </div>

  <pre><code class="html"><%= '<h1 class="slab">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h1>' %>
<%= '<h2 class="slab">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h2>' %>
<%= '<h3 class="slab">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h3>' %>
<%= '<h4 class="slab">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h4>' %>
<%= '<h5 class="slab">BuzzFeed is the social news and entertainment company</h5>' %></code></pre>

</section>

<section class="xs-mb5 xs-pb2">

  <h2 class="xs-mb2 bold">Emphasis</h2>

  <p class="xs-mb4">Use the following html tags and utility classes to add emphasis to blocks of text.</p>

  <div class="xs-mb4">
    <p class="xs-mb1">.<code class="js-highlight">regular</code></p>
    <p class="bold xs-mb1"><span class="regular">BuzzFeed is the</span> social news and entertainment company</p>
